Why?  What need has god of property right contracts between his pet humans?  Essentially a marriage is a property right contract for support and exclusive breeding rights.  Does this serve god in some way?  I fail to see how, he made adam and eve but he didn’t marry them in the garden, so why once he has cast us out and fears our power does he need us to contract our relations?  Could it be that the property right contract was an important part of society and the need to control the females into obedience to their husbands so that the contracts would be kept and thus economic ties maintained was important to ancient culture?  Was the social bonds made by marriage more important then the human rights they tromped all over?  Are we now 4000 years later romanticizing it into something so we don’t get all erratic over it now?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Children are entitled to birth within the bonds of matrimony and to be reared by a father and mother who honor marital vows with complete fidelity.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> This is an implicit impeachment of unwed parenting.  Yet single parenting is far more prevalent in xian homes than in atheist ones.  How odd.  I know couples that are not married but have been together for decades and their kids are fine.  I also know married couples that are awful and the children are far worse for being forced to live in an acrimonious home.  How condescendingly presumptuous that there is only one road to Rome and all others inferior or defective.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Happiness in family life is most likely to be achieved when founded upon the teachings of Jesus Christ. Successful marriages and families are established and maintained on principles of faith, prayer, repentance, forgiveness, respect, love, compassion, work and wholesome recreational activities. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> Blatantly untrue and unsupported by the facts.  The marriages founded on Christ fail far more frequently than those of atheist origin.  Furthermore, the self-righteous word <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>wholesome</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is itself an ambiguous and threatening term.  It permits the morals of another to hold some type of superiority and dictatorial power over everyone else.  Very offensive.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>By divine design, fathers are to preside over their families in love and righteousness and are responsible to provide the necessities of life and protection for their families. Mothers are primarily responsible for the nurture of their children. In these sacred responsibilities, fathers and mothers are obligated to help one another as equal partners.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> Equals, yet some are more equal than others.  The man has all that burden of telling everyone what to do.  How awful for him.  The woman is but to pump out babies and serve slavishly the will of her lord and master. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :x --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/sick.gif ALT=":x"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   (Puke!) <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :x --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/sick.gif ALT=":x"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   This is just plain STUPID!  What design makes a man superior?  Are they inherently more intelligent than women?  Do they lead because they are smarter?  Stronger?  Wiser?  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>BULLSHIT!</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  If god designed man to lead, then men would be smarter.  Here’s a fact for you, the highest intelligence population is 2/3 more frequently male than female.  Does that validate god’s design if men are smarter?  Here’s another fact for you, the lowest intelligence population is 2/3 more frequently male than female.  How does that add up?  It implies that intellegence is a female sex linked trait and the women by virtue of having 2 chromosomes to the man’s one have a more normalized (less extreme) IQ range.  Net result?  Overall equals across the population.  What a crappy engineer god is to set it up like that when he could have just made it a MALE sex linked trait and then men would logically rule by virtue of greater intelligence.  <br>
<br>
How about some fiscal logic?  If my wife is an accountant or a tax attorney who the hell am I the golf pro to tell her what to do with the money?  Shouldn’t I listen to her greater expertise and respect the skills she brings that I lack?  What if she is a successful news caster and makes $250K a year and I am a toll booth attendant making $19K, should I knock her up and make her quit to be a mommy because I am male and must provide for the family?  That would be a divorce from sensibility.  It makes me sick to see such total abdication from personal responsibility and cognitive diligence.  I am amazed that xians think themselves remotely moral at all if everything good comes from god’s design and everything bad is of Satan, then what do you actually contribute?  You are pawns being moved by invisible hands and pretending it is freewill, yet it is really freewill and you just scapegoat your personal irresponsibility.<br>
<br>
Quit kicking the equal rights and protections of others in the groin and act like equals.  Take personal responsibility and carry your weight like so many generations of hard working, intelligent and amazing women have done.  You disrespect their efforts and painfully won equality and I would question your deserving the fruits of their labors.  Just like the rewards of science, the fruit of secular labor is shared unselfishly with all, unlike your petty gods torturous sadism.<br>
<br>
Man I can get worked up sometimes.  Who the hell left this soapbox here and how the hell did I end up on it?<br>
